longBusinessSummary: Joshua Gold Resources Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. The company explores for gold and graphite deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the C1 Mortimer Property comprising 37 contiguous staked mining claims; and the Chewett Property that includes nine contiguous single cells staked mining claims. The company was formerly known as Enhanced Energy Solutions Corp. and changed its name to Joshua Gold Resources Inc. in October 2016. Joshua Gold Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Woodstock, Canada.
